README

# myMacOsTools

This repository contains a collection of tools/script for MacOS.

## Tools

## scripts

### myCleanScript.sh

This script will clean cache of system and applications.
Empty the trash.

### myDownloadClean.sh

this script will clean the download folder.
he send a notification by email 10 minutes before cleaning.
update homebrew and remove old versions.

## Installation

Clone the repository to your local machine and navigate to the directory:

Add execution permissions to the scripts:

```bash
chmod +x myCleanScript.sh
chmod +x myDownloadClean.sh
```

Add script in cron job:

```bash
crontab -e
```

Add the following line to the file:

```bash
0 0 * * * /path/to/myCleanScript.sh
0 0 * * * /path/to/myDownloadClean.sh
```
